author: Al Jazeera
title: California reports coronavirus death dating to early February
description: The deaths, weeks earlier than previously reported, may shift the timeline of when the virus spread across the US.
content:
Health officials in California now say two people in that state died with the coronavirus weeks earlier than has previously been reported.
Officials in Santa Clara County said late on Tuesday that the people died in their homes on February 6 and February 17.… [+3585 chars]
